SUMMARY:Game Night: Bridge Instructional Play Session I 
LOCATION:The Muse
DESCRIPTION:Category: Sports & Games\nPrice: Free\nStatus: Waitlist Only\nE
 vent URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/174007\n\nDiscover the a
 rt and strategy of Bridge in a thoughtfully designed two-part instructiona
 l series for members. Our expert instructor\, Zach Grossack\, will guide 
 members through the fundamentals\, offering tips\, strategies\, and techni
 ques designed for beginners and intermediate players alike.\n\nEach sessio
 n is relaxed and hands-on\, offering the opportunity to practice bidding\,
  refine strategy\, and build confidence at the table with personalized gui
 dance. Look forward to a welcoming environment to learn\, improve\, and en
 joy the timeless art of Bridge alongside fellow members.\n\n*This event is
  complimentary and reserved for members only. Please note that this is a t
 wo-part series\; registration for the first session on March 10th will aut
 omatically enroll you in the second session on March 17th\, ensuring a coh
 esive learning experience across both evenings. Guests are invited to arri
 ve at 5:30PM to settle in with a bite and beverage on the 'House before th
 e class begins promptly at 6:00 PM.
