  strategy of Bridge in a thoughtfully designed two-part instructional seri
 es for members. Our expert instructor\, Zach Grossack\, will guide member
 s through the fundamentals\, offering tips\, strategies\, and techniques d
 esigned for beginners and intermediate players alike.\n\nEach session is r
 elaxed and hands-on\, offering the opportunity to practice bidding\, refin
 e strategy\, and build confidence at the table with personalized guidance.
  Look forward to a welcoming environment to learn\, improve\, and enjoy th
 e timeless art of Bridge alongside fellow members.\n\n*This event is compl
 imentary and reserved for members only. Please note that this is a two-par
 t series\; registration for the first session on March 10th will automatic
 ally enroll you in the second session on March 17th\, ensuring a cohesive 
 learning experience across both evenings. Guests are invited to arrive at 
 5:30PM to settle in with a bite and beverage on the 'House before the clas
 s begins promptly at 6:00 PM.
