SUMMARY:Community Dinner Table
LOCATION:Café Q
DESCRIPTION:Category: Member Mixer\nPrice: Free\nAvailability: 3 spots left
 \nStatus: Available\nEvent URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/16
 6021\n\nStart your week in good company with the Café Q Community dinner 
 table for members-only. Set aside for those looking to expand their social
  circle over a shared meal\, this gathering is all about good food\, livel
 y conversation\, and meaningful connections. Pull up a chair\, and savor t
 he experience—because nothing brings people together quite like a great 
 meal.\n\n*This event is reserved for members only. An advance charge of $2
 4 per member contributes to communal appetizers available upon seating. Me
 mbers are responsible for à la carte entrées\, desserts\, and beverages\
 , plus taxes and fees. Cancellations made within 24 hours of the event\, o
 r failure to attend will be subject to the Café Q's surcharge policy.
URL:https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/166021
CATEGORIES:Member Mixer
